items.name: Healthy Mind
explicitMods: Increases and Reductions to Life in Radius are Transformed to apply to Mana at 200% of their value
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: For the ambitious, flesh is a limitation.

items.name: Watcher's Eye
explicitMods: Cannot be Blinded while affected by Precision
Gain 6% of Maximum Mana as Extra Maximum Energy Shield while affected by Clarity
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: One by one, they stood their ground against a creature
they had no hope of understanding, let alone defeating,
and one by one, they became a part of it.

items.name: Forbidden Flesh
explicitMods: Allocates Augury of Penitence if you have the matching modifier on Forbidden Flame
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The bodies of those wholly subsumed by the Tangle
continue to merge and mutate and cry out for release...

items.name: Elegant Hubris
explicitMods:
Commissioned 88160 coins to commemorate Victario
Passives in radius are Conquered by the Eternal Empire
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: They believed themselves better than the past, but that confidence brought about nightmare.

items.typeLine: Notable Small Cluster Jewel of the Student
enchantMods: Added Small Passive Skills grant: 6% increased maximum Mana
explicitMods: Added Small Passive Skills also grant: +5 to Intelligence
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Small, Medium or Large Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Added passives do not interact with jewel radiuses. Right click to remove from the Socket.

items.name: Split Personality
explicitMods:
This Jewel's Socket has 25% increased effect per Allocated Passive Skill between
it and your Class' starting location
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: You need not go looking for a second opinion.

items.name: Forbidden Flame
explicitMods: Allocates Augury of Penitence if you have the matching modifier on Forbidden Flesh
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The minds of those studied utterly by the Cleansing Fire
continue to think and dream and beg for silence...

items.name: Might of the Meek
explicitMods: 50% increased Effect of non-Keystone Passive Skills in Radius
Notable Passive Skills in Radius grant nothing
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: Enough mice can kill a wolf.
